 section of the goals.\r\n\r\nLet me write a concise update.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI compression experiment revealed a critical insight: tokens with freq�160 and CFI=1.00 are metaprogramming artifacts, not causal signals. The next step is to implement the hybrid scoring formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) to distinguish \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\".\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nUpdate the pending goals to include the hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C) derived from the constant-format problem insight.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: ## Pending\r\n- [ ] Hybrid CFIA-Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n- [ ] Distinguish \"constant format\" (freq�%^160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)\r\n- [ ] Implement CFI filtering to remove metaprogramming contamination\r\n- [ ] Wire Breakaway pulses to real TemporalAttention backend\r\n- [ ] Design actual compression network (currently only analyzed text invariants)\r\nnew_text: ## Pending\r\n- [ ] Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n  - Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n  - Test: does this distinguish \"constant format\" (freq�160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)?\r\n  - Run: 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n- [ ] Implement CFI filtering to remove metaprogramming contamination\r\n- [ ] Wire Breakaway pulses to real TemporalAttention backend\r\n- [ ] Design actual compression network (currently only analyzed text invariants)\r\nfile: state/goals.md\r\n```\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\r\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:12:02"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2804,"aggregated":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 141145\r\n\r\n## Applied Mutations\r\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\r\nRejected: research/HYBRID_SCORING_EXPERIMENT.md (missing)\r\n\r\n## LLM Response\r\n<think>\r\nLet me review the current state